node.text:
Diving headfirst into the weekend like… ☁️ Wingsuit flying (or wingsuiting) is the sport of flying through the air using a wingsuit which adds surface area to the human body to enable a significant increase in lift. 

This wingsuit flight was shoot in Montserrat Natural Park, a multi-peaked mountain range near Barcelona, in Catalonia, Spain.

"Montserrat" literally means "serrated (like the common handsaw) mountain" in Catalan. It describes its peculiar aspect with a multitude of rock formations that are visible from a great distance. The mountain is composed of strikingly pink conglomerate, a form of sedimentary rock.

📽 @daniroman_ @fredfugen @vincent.cotte @bras.noir
📍Montserrant, Spain

node.text:
Spotting sea snakes with @brodiemoss 😳

“Sea snakes normally avoid humans but this time of year they become very active, sexually frustrated and potentially aggressive as they search for a mate 🐍 like this old fella who appeared from the ocean floor and followed me around on my paddle board before disappearing 😅”

What would you do in this situation? 😱

📽 @brodiemoss
📍Australia

Somewhere in Japan 🇯🇵 From 1 to 10, which is your favorite @nature scenery and why?

Swipe to see its breathtaking views and save this post for your Japan trip! 📝

@Nature 𝗗𝗲𝘀𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝗝𝗮𝗽𝗮𝗻
1. Gifu Prefecture
2. Yoshino Mountain, Nara
3. Shirahige Shrine, Shiga
4. Mt. Fuji, Shizuoka
5. Colony of Mitsumata, Kyoto
6. Gujō, Gifu
7. Nagano Prefecture
8. Mie Prefecture
9. Mt. Fuji, Shizuoka
10. Tottori Sand Dunes, Tottori

📸 @ag.lr.88
📍 Japan

node.text:
The Land of Legends in Turkey 😍 Unleash your adventurous spirit at Turkey’s first magical kingdom. Packed to the brim with entertainment to suit any taste, a holiday here ensures a legendary and unforgettable experience for all the family. From the on-site theme park to the Venetian-style canals, the Land of Legends is sure to live up to its name.

📽 @waelalteen
📍Antalya, Turkey
🎶 Hailey Barnes & Calvin Jenkins - Lovely
